        <p>Singh, in his analysis, proposed that type 2 can convert to type 3, and it is not a wise option to delay surgery in PPC cases.</p>
        <p>
<bold>Schroeder's Classification </bold>
</p>
        <p>He classified PPC in pediatric patients based on the obstruction in the red reflex through the pupil<xref ref-type="bibr" rid="article-140544.r21">[21]</xref></p>
